      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Whether your garden is large, medium or small, a garden storage shed is a necessity because it can house more than your gardening tools. However, choosing the right <strong><a href="http://gardenstorageshedplans.com/recommend/" target="_blank">garden storage shed plans</a></strong> and design that looks good with your house and the rest of your yard is very important. A wooden storage shed is a perfect option when it comes to value, appeal and durability.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a target="_blank"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-116" title="WOOD-5-horz" src="http://gardenstorageshedplans.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/WOOD-5-horz.jpg" alt="" width="1060" height="303" /></a></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Wooden Storage Sheds</strong></p>
<p><strong>6 Outstanding Advantages of Wooden Storage Sheds</strong></p>
<p>1. Using wood for storage sheds encourages eco-friendliness. People who want to help save mother earth use wood because it is a renewable material. Many nations around the world have laws that require a replacement tree for every tree that gets cut.</p>
<p>2. Wood is cheap and durable to stand all kinds of weather elements including sun, rain, wind and snow. There are paints or stains that protect wood surface from damp weather to make it last.</p>
<p>3. Wood sheds are easy to modify. You can add more shelves using simple carpenter tools if you need more space to stack-up boxes and other items that you don’t use very often in the house.</p>
<p>4. Wooden garden sheds can add value to your property. You can customize the look and make it appear as a little version of your house to create a designer look.</p>
<p>5. Wood blends in with any garden environment because of its natural color. A beautifully designed wooden shed can serve not only as storage but also as a place to spend time leisurely, make new plans for the future, work on your hobby or as a playhouse for children.</p>
<p>6. Slabs of wood can be found anywhere in your neighborhood or local factories if you are resourceful enough. There are dismantled wooden structures just waiting for someone to bargain. All you need is to get a <strong>garden shed plan</strong> and follow the procedure from there. That is only – if you want to save more money. If your budget allows it, maybe you would desire to buy first hand materials, of course.</p>
<p>Outdoor <strong>garden shed plans</strong> are available for making sheds out of different materials such as vinyl, plastic and metal; but most people prefer sheds made from wood particularly the western red cedar wood. Cedar is plainly beautiful and it has a very inviting smell. Other materials used in making sheds cannot offer the same benefits and flexibility like wood. They provide basically the space needed for storage but they don’t have the beauty, charm and versatility of wooden storage sheds.</p>
<p>You must look for some <strong>garden storage shed plans</strong> designed for woodwork before you start building your dream wooden shed. One of the best places where the best wood storage shed designs are found is My Shed Plans. Would you prefer a metal or plastic shed when all that you can smell inside is the gas of the lawnmower and the aroma from stored pesticides? It may be the last place you and your kids want to be.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://gardenstorageshedplans.com/recommend/" target="_blank">Hurry! Take a look at the most beautiful garden storage shed plans created for woodwork here. </a></strong></p>
]]></content:encoded>
